            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4 max-w-md mx-auto pt-4">
                <div class="space-y-2 text-left">
                    <label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">ชื่อเล่นของคุณ</label>
                    <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="ระบุชื่อของคุณ..." class="w-full p-3.5 bg-slate-950/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl focus:border-red-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-red-500 outline-none text-slate-100 font-medium">
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-2 text-left">
                    <label class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">เลือกไลฟ์สไตล์ (Archetype)</label>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                        <button onclick="selectArchetype('gamer')" id="arch-gamer" class="p-3 bg-slate-950/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl hover:border-red-500/50 hover:bg-slate-950/60 text-left transition-all text-xs font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">
                            🎮 สายแอร์ฉ่ำสิงหน้าจอ
                        </button>
                        <button onclick="selectArchetype('boba')" id="arch-boba" class="p-3 bg-slate-950/40 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl hover:border-red-500/50 hover:bg-slate-950/60 text-left transition-all text-xs font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">
